OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying dry,
OL,6,Fwith late evening sunshine. Remaining
OL,7,Fbreezy along the coast. Some showers
OL,8,Fpossible in the early hours of
OL,9,FThursday morning, particularly in the
OL,10,Fwest.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FA fine day, with plenty of
OL,13,Fsunshine and temperatures increasing
OL,14,Fagain. Brisk southeasterly winds
OL,15,Fexpected, with some strong gusts along
OL,16,Fthe coast. Isolated thundery showers
OL,17,Fpossible in the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
